pageContext.claim: “The one thing I forgot to say, which was the most important. You know that every single ballot she did went to Biden. You know that, right? Do you know that, by the way, Brad? Every single ballot that she did through the machines at early, early in the morning went to Biden. Did you know that, Ryan?”
pageContext.analysis: "That’s not accurate, Mr. President," secretary of state counsel Ryan Germany replied. "The numbers that we are showing are accurate."
